        <text>C.O.M.P.A.S.S Station</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_compass_station_descr">
        <text>Compact Omnidirectional Modulated Portable Anomalous Slipstreaming Station \n \n
            After Strelok's raid on the CNPP ended with the destruction of the Monolith Control
            Center, the path to the heart of the Zone opened. Stalkers were able to scavenge the
            teleport technology used by Monolithians. Originally powered by the Generators
            themselves, the technology was reverse-engineered to use a powerful artifact instead.
            The lack of original blueprints and a stable connection to the noosphere made the
            device stationary and added a lengthy calibration requirement, but you won't find a
            faster way to travel around the Zone. \n \n
            %c[d_red]The device's anomalous origin can sometimes produce unexpected results\n
        </text>
    </string>
